    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1931-07-11T12:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1931-07-11T12:00:00-05:00" n="768"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d768">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">825.00/661: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Chile</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Norweb</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Santiago</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-07-11T12:00:00-05:00"
                            >July 11, 1931—noon</date>.<lb/>[Received 2:40 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>64. In view of the Government’s serious financial difficulties and in order to
                    draft the services of the country’s most prominent men to meet the situation,
                    the President yesterday requested the Cabinet to resign, with the exception of
                    the Ministers of War and Navy. He has <pb facs="1016" n="902" xml:id="pg_902"/>
                    asked Francisco Garcesgana, President of the Central Bank, to form a new cabinet
                    but the latter is having difficulties in getting the men he wants.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">norweb</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
